room_title: Escape room "Sherlock’s Library" by ALL IN Adventures in Tuscaloosa
room_address: 1800 Mcfarland Blvd. E, Suite 302 Tuscaloosa, AL 35404
room_description:
You enter 221B Baker Street, London and into Sherlock’s Library. Everything is quiet. Too quiet. You rummage through Sherlock’s things and realize he’s on a case and needs your help. With your excellent deductive reasoning skills, 50 minutes should just about do it to solve the case.
Also available in an easier difficulty level (2).
